vation. The event brings together startups, CEOs, investors, tech leaders and all of the digital transformation players who are shaping the future of the Internet. The annual technology conference, also known as VivaTech, was founded in 2016 by Publicis Groupe and Groupe Les Echos and is dedicated to promoting innovation and startups. (Photo by Chesnot/Getty Images)]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[8th Viva Technology : Day One In Paris]]></media:title></media:content></item><item><title><![CDATA[Life is Strange spiritual successor delayed to avoid Life is Strange sequel]]></title><description type="html"><![CDATA[<p> <em>《失落的记录：绽放与愤怒》</em>是<a data-i13n="cpos:1;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/tag/life-is-strange/"><ins>《奇异人生》</ins></a>开发商推出的一款全新游戏。它被描述为该系列的精神继承者，原定于 2024 年底推出。然而，发行商 Don&#39;t Nod 选择推迟<em>《失落的记录：绽放与愤怒》</em> ，并于 2025 年初发行。</p><p>事实上，延迟很大程度上是由于另一家工作室的新《奇异人生》<a data-i13n="cpos:2;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/gaming/"><ins>游戏</ins></a>造成的。 <a data-i13n="cpos:3;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/were-officially-getting-another-life-is-strange-game-this-fall-193230167.html"><em><ins>《奇异人生：双重曝光》</ins></em></a>标志着原版游戏主角马克斯·考菲尔德的回归。由 Square Enix 和开发商 Deck Nine Games 制作的续作将于 10 月登陆<a data-i13n="cpos:4;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/gaming/pc/"><ins>PC</ins></a> 、 <a data-i13n="cpos:5;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/gaming/playstation/"><ins>PlayStation 5</ins></a>和<a data-i13n="cpos:6;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/gaming/xbox/"><ins>Xbox Series X/S</ins></a> ，并计划稍后<a data-i13n="cpos:7;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/gaming/nintendo/"><ins>在 Switch</ins></a>上发布。 </p><span id="end-legacy-contents"></span><div id="e8ef66cba6384be0a5b0548f36f7e035"><div style="left:0;width:100%;height:0;position:relative;padding-bottom:56.25%;"><iframe src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/A2aNUtMUvIM?rel=0" style="top:0;left:0;width:100%;height:100%;position:absolute;border:0;" allowfullscreen="" scrolling="no" data-embed-domain="www.youtube.com"></iframe></div></div><p> Don’t Nod 表示，在“对行业最新趋势和发展进行深入评估”后，它希望给<em>《Lost Records: Bloom &amp; Rage》</em>一些喘息空间，以取得成功。但首席执行官奥斯卡·吉尔伯特 (Oskar Guilbert) 的一句话使这一推理更加明确。吉尔伯特<a data-i13n="cpos:8;pos:1" href="https://www.actusnews.com/en/dontnod/pr/2024/06/28/don_t-nod-optimizes-the-release-window-for-its-next-leading-game-for-lost-records-bloom-et-rage-and-don_t-nod-reports-on-its"><ins>在一份声明中表示</ins></a>：“我们知道许多粉丝都在热切地等待这款游戏，就像最近宣布的《奇异人生》的下一期一样。” “让我们在我们建立的大型社区中为这两款游戏提供玩家需要的空间。”</p><p>虽然这次更新可能会让那些期待<em>《Lost Records》</em>的人感到失望，但这是一个明智的决定。它为球迷提供了充足的时间来体验这两款游戏，而不会出现太多重叠。</p><p>与此同时，Don’t Nod 认为<em>《放逐者：新伊甸之魂</em>》是今年早些时候推出的一款令人惊讶的情感动作角色扮演游戏， <a data-i13n="cpos:9;pos:1" href="https://www.forbes.com/sites/krisholt/2024/02/13/banishers-ghosts-of-new-eden-review-a-beautiful-dark-love-story-for-valentines-day/"><ins>我非常喜欢</ins></a>，它将提高其盈利，尤其是从长远来看。去年年底，该公司还发布了一款深思熟虑的攀岩<a data-i13n="cpos:10;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/its-a-golden-age-of-puzzle-games-even-for-people-who-suck-at-puzzle-games-130024186.html"><ins>益智游戏</ins></a><a data-i13n="cpos:11;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/best-relaxing-video-games-140048572.html"><em><ins>“Jusant”</ins></em></a> 。</p>本文最初发表在 Engadget 上：https://www.engadget.com/life-is-strange-spiritual-successor-delayed-to-avoid-life-is-strange-sequel-124553471.html?src=rss]] >; </description><link/><![CDATA[https://www.engadget.com/life-is-strange-spiritual-successor-delayed-to-avoid-life-is-strange-sequel-124553471.html?src=rss]]><source_id> engadget_479</source_id><guid ispermalink="false"> 6b257ffc-da4d-4cea-8732-150b2d0b0408 </guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[Kris Holt]]></dc:creator><source/><![CDATA[Engadget]]><dc:publisher><![CDATA[Engadget]]></dc:publisher><dc:rightsholder><![CDATA[Engadget]]></dc:rightsholder><pubDate> Fri, 28 Jun 2024 12:45:53 +0000</pubDate><ingested> 1719578460</ingested><modified> 2024-06-28T12:41:04+00:00 </modified><category><![CDATA[Video Games]]></category><category><![CDATA[site|engadget]]></